### 基础变量配置
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8787/api
@apiKey = your_test_api_key_here

### AI-01: 获取系统自发现信息 (Info)
GET {{baseUrl}}/info
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### F-01: 获取所有任务 (支持搜索及基础筛选)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?q=咖啡
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### F-07: 任务列表多维度筛选验证 (标签名、优先级、状态)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?tag_name=紧急&priority=high&status=in_progress
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### F-02: 创建一个 AI 生成的任务 (带元数据与溯源，标签自动创建)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "分析新版 API 文档",
  "description": "- [ ] 阅读文档\n- [ ] 总结变更",
  "priority": "high",
  "category_id": 1,
  "source": "openclaw",
  "tags": ["紧急", "文档更新"],
  "metadata": "{\"reason\": \"doc_update\", \"ref_url\": \"https://example.com/api\"}",
  "due_date": "2026-03-05T10:00:00.000Z"
}

### F-06: 修改已有任务 (更新字段并关联新标签)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "购买两种咖啡豆",
  "priority": "high",
  "tags": ["采购", "紧急"],
  "due_date": "2026-03-02T12:00:00.000Z"
}

### F-03: 标记任务完成 (验证周期逻辑)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/3/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### F-08: 标签格式校验测试 (应被拒绝，包含特殊字符)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid Tag !"
}

### R-01: 模拟云端提醒检查 (Bark)
POST {{baseUrl}}/remind/check?channel=cloud
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### R-02: 模拟 Agent 提醒检查 (No Bark)
POST {{baseUrl}}/remind/check?channel=agent
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### S-01: 无效鉴权测试 (应返回 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/info
Authorization: Bearer WRONG_KEY

### T-02: 非法时间格式校验 (应被拒绝)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试时间校验",
  "due_date": "2026/03/05 10:00:00"
}
